        "start": 0,
        "end": 2
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_125_000143",
    "sentence": "液父徽，初尚郜國；徽卒，降蕭升。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_125_000144",
    "sentence": "柳渾",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_125_000145",
    "sentence": "柳渾，字夷曠，襄州人，其先自河東徙焉。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "襄州",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 7,
        "end": 9
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_125_000146",
    "sentence": "六代祖惔，梁僕射。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_125_000147",
    "sentence": "渾少孤，父慶休，官至渤海丞，而誌學棲貧。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_125_000148",
    "sentence": "天寶初，舉進士，補單父尉。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_125_000149",
    "sentence": "至德中，為江西采訪使皇甫侁判官，累除衢州司馬。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "皇甫侁",
